'''''Minotaur Kneeling over Sleeping Girl''''' is a 1933 etching by [[Pablo Picasso]]. It is the first example among several works to be realized through the remaining part of the decade where Picasso used the theme of the legendary [[Minoan civilization|Minoan]] creature, the [[Minotaur]].

